ruct | ✅ EXISTS |\n| DefaultJWTConfig() | ✅ EXISTS |\n| Config validation | ✅ EXISTS |\n\n#### 3.5 JWT Middleware ✅ PASS\n\n| Component | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| JWTMiddleware struct | ✅ EXISTS |\n| Authentication handler | ✅ EXISTS |\n| Claims extraction | ✅ EXISTS |\n| Context propagation | ✅ EXISTS |\n\n---\n\n## Part 4: Build & Test Verification\n\n### Build Status: ✅ PASS\n```\ngo build ./...  # SUCCESS\n```\n\n### Test Status: ✅ PASS\n```\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...  # ALL PASS (35+ tests)\n```\n\n### Test Coverage: ⚠️ PARTIAL\n- API Types: ✅ Well tested\n- Router: ⚠️ No test files\n- Client-Go: ⚠️ No test files\n\n---\n\n## Summary Table\n\n| Category | Score | Critical Issues |\n|----------|-------|-----------------|\n| API Types | ✅ 100% | None |\n| Client-Go Clientset | ⚠️ 50% | Missing Discovery, constructors |\n| Client-Go Typed | ⚠️ 70% | Missing DeleteCollection, RESTClient |\n| Client-Go Scheme | ❌ 0% | Package not implemented |\n| Client-Go Informers | ⚠️ 60% | Missing advanced features |\n| Client-Go Listers | ✅ 95% | Minor expansion issues |\n| Client-Go Structure | ❌ 30% | Non-compliant layout |\n| JWT Implementation | ✅ 95% | Build fix applied |\n| Build Status | ✅ PASS | Fixed JWTMetrics issue |\n| Test Status | ✅ PASS | API tests passing |\n\n---\n\n## Critical Findings\n\n1. **JWTMetrics Missing** - FIXED: Added JWTMetrics type to jwt_types.go\n2. **Client-Go Scheme Package** - NOT IMPLEMENTED: Required for proper client initialization\n3. **REST Client Implementation** - IN-MEMORY ONLY: Uses custom store instead of Kubernetes API\n4. **Module Configuration** - MISSING: No go.mod for client-go submodule\n5. **Directory Layout** - NON-COMPLIANT: Doesn't follow standard code-generator output\n\n---\n\n## Recommendations\n\n1. **For Client-Go**: Use Kubernetes code-generator to regenerate from API types\n2. **For Testing**: Add unit tests for router package (AR-011)\n3. **For Structure**: Align directory structure with spec\n4. **For Module**: Create separate go.mod for client-go if needed as submodule\n\nEOF\n","description":"Create final verification report"},"output":"# Implementation Verification Report\n## AR-011: Router JWT Authentication & Issuance + Client-Go Library\n\n### Executive Summary\n\nThis report verifies the implementation against the spec defined in `deployment/client-go.md` \nand the AR-011 requirements for Router JWT authentication.\n\n---\n\n## Part 1: API Types Verification ✅\n\n### Location: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n| Requirement | Status | Evidence |\n|-------------|--------|----------|\n| SchemeGroupVersion = runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1 | ✅ PASS | register.go:27-30 |\n| AgentRuntime type with +genclient | ✅ PASS | agentruntime_types.go:246-272 |\n| AgentRuntimeList type | ✅ PASS | agentruntime_types.go:277-285 |\n| CodeInterpreter type with +genclient | ✅ PASS | codeinterpreter_types.go:193-216 |\n| CodeInterpreterList type | ✅ PASS | codeinterpreter_types.go:221-229 |\n| REST resource plural: agentruntimes | ✅ PASS | agentruntime_types.go:250 |\n| REST resource plural: codeinterpreters | ✅ PASS | codeinterpreter_types.go:197 |\n\n**Test Results:** All API type tests PASS (35+ test cases)\n\n---\n\n## Part 2: Client-Go Library Verification\n\n### Reference Implementation Location: `workspaces/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/`\n\n#### 2.1 Clientset ✅ PARTIAL\n\n| Spec Requirement | Status | Location |\n|------------------|--------|----------|\n| Interface with Discovery() | ❌ MISSING | - |\n| Interface with RuntimeV1alpha1() | ✅ EXISTS | clientset.go:8 |\n| Clientset struct | ✅ EXISTS | real.go:9-11 |\n| NewForConfig() | ⚠️ STUB | real.go:13-15 (returns empty) |\n| NewForConfigAndClient() | ❌ MISSING | - |\n| NewForConfigOrDie() | ❌ MISSING | - |\n| New() | ❌ MISSING | - |\n\n#### 2.2 Typed Client ⚠️ PARTIAL\n\n| Spec Requirement | Status | Notes |\n|------------------|--------|-------|\n| RuntimeV1alpha1Inte